introduce VAT administration this year, and the other three next
year.
</P>
<P>
South African Customs spokesman Christo Henning, who earlier
announced the complete closure of the five border posts, confirmed
only commercial travellers would be affected.
</P>
<P>
Henning also cited security concerns including rampant crime and
the influx of smuggled and fake goods as reasons for restricting
commercial exit points.
</P>
