Romanian people and the Romanian government are the most eager of
all people of all countries in the zone to belong to the
Euro-Atlantic structures."
</P>
<P>
According to the Romanian prime minister, Gore assured him
"if Romania continues its reforms, it will be included in the
second wave."  
