<HEADLINE> State Leader Congratulates Developers of New Super Computer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Vice-Premier Zou Jiahua checked
out the "Yinhe-3" super computer after it passed State appraisal
here today, and congratulated the researchers on their success.
</P>
<P>
After hearing reports and watching the computer perform, Zou
said researchers should be creative in the hi-tech field and be
skillful in absorbing overseas expertise for the development of
