well-received by all parties including the Turkish government," he
told reporters after a social function here.
</P>
<P>
D-8 aims to enhance economic ties among member countries to
ensure a strong and effective grouping irrespective of their
political ideology.
</P>
<P>
The grouping held its inaugural summit in Istanbul, Turkey, on
Sunday and Malaysian Prime Minister Mahathir Mohamad, who is
abroad for a long vacation, was among several leaders of the D-8
member countries to attend the summit.  
