<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Share prices finished mixed on
the Singapore market while the benchmark Straits Times Industrials
Index rose by 17.83 points to close at 2002.97 today.
</P>
<P>
Despite its marginal increase, the total market volume was
still thin at 95.83 million units, worth 279.55 million Singapore
dollars (about 195.49 million U.S. dollars). Declines overtook
advances by 197 to 113 while 317 other counters remained
unchanged.
</P>
