cents to finish at 15.4 Singapore dollars. Local car distributor
Cycle &AMP; Carriage (C&AMP;C) increased by 70 cents to end at 14.9
Singapore dollars. The Singapore Press Holdings (SPH) Foreign and
Samanda Holdings gained 60 cents each to close at 28.6 and 11.9
Singapore dollars respectively.
