<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 19 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today dropped 17 HK dollars to close at 3,143 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 340.79 dollars a troy ounce,
down 1.9 US dollar at today's exchange rate of one US dollar to
7.7415 HK
dollars. 
</P>
</TEXT>
