<BODY>
<HEADLINE> French Insurance Company Opens Representative Office in Sichuan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, June 19 (Xinhua) -- AXA-UAP/National Mutual
International Property Ltd of France opened a representative
office in Chengdu, capital of southwest China's Sichuan Province,
recently.
</P>
<P>
The representative office is the ninth overseas-backed
financial organization that is authorized to handle business in
this southwestern Chinese province, said a local official.
</P>
<P>
The French company has opened business offices in more than 50
countries and regions and is entrusted by clients to help manage
their assets worth 500 billion U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
According to rules, the trans-national French company is
required to wait two more years to start insurance services in
Sichuan.  
</P>
</TEXT>
