<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Zambian Manufacturers are urged to
consider exploiting the large market of the Democratic Republic
of Congo for their exports.
</P>
<P>
There is need for Zambian manufacturers to look into the
possibility of exploiting the Conglolese market as it is opening
up for various goods, said Jennifer Kaunda, managing director of
Star Spin Company on Wednesday in Kitwe of Copperbelt province
bordering Congo.
