<HEADLINE> South China Province to Build Cable Bridge </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Construction on a cable-stayed
bridge with a 634-meter span is scheduled to begin in Haikou at
the end of the year.
</P>
<P>
