meters wide, is estimated to cost 667 million yuan. Financing
includes 50 million US dollars in loans from Japan.
</P>
<P>
The project is scheduled to be completed within three years,
and is expected to help ease traffic jams in the capital city.
</P>
<P>
It is the first urban construction project in the city to
invite international bids. 
