<HEADLINE> UNFPA Assists Nepal in Population Program </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, June 19 (Xinhua) -- A Memorandum of Understanding
(MOU) was signed here Wednesday between the Nepali government and
the United Nations Population Fund (UNFPA) to assist Nepal in its
population program.
