<HEADLINE> Brussels Conference Looks at Communications </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, June 18 (Xinhua) -- A conference on communications
here today aims to increase understanding and awareness of the
important roles of advanced communications in the building of an
information society.
