in Washington the flexibility in the U.S. immigration laws.
</P>
<P>
At a press conference, Nicaraguan Foreign Minister Emilio
Alvarez announced today that the visit of the Nicaraguan president
aims to offer his support for those Nicaraguans who are living in
the United States.
</P>
