<HEADLINE> Zabel Wins Second Stage in Tour of Switzerland </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, June 18 (Xinhua) -- Erik Zabel of Germany won a wild
sprint to take the second stage of the Tour of Switzerland in
Basle, Switzerland, on Wednesday.
